data.description: SELLERS OFFERING 3% CONCESSIONS FOR RATE BUYDOWN/CLOSING COSTS. Centrally located 3bd/2ba Main house with 230 sq ft guest house with a bathroom and no HOA. Close to hospitals, AZ Center, sports stadiums, symphony hall, light rail, parks, airport and hiking nearby at Camelback Mtn. The home has a welcoming great room that leads right into the beautifully updated kitchen with quartz countertops, pendant lighting, stainless steel appliances and tile/vinyl throughout the whole downstairs. The primary suite is downstairs with a large walk-in closet and its own ensuite. Stairs were redone with vinyl. The upstairs has 2 bedrooms with walk-in closets and a hall bathroom. Guest house has its own AC unit, bathroom, and beautiful vinyl flooring. Roof replaced 2022 & new AC on the main house in 2019.
